----- DATA RELATED --------------------------------------------------

----- MISCELLANEOUS FUNCTIONS ---------------------------------------

string freemed_config_value ( string key )
	description:
		Gets a value from the FreeMED configuration registry.
		(It also caches the values so additional SQL calls
		are not needed.)
	global dependencies:
		$sql from lib/freemed.php
	returns:
		value of specified configuration variable, or NULL
		if that key does not exist
		

